title: Android 12L comes to Galaxy S5 via unofficial LineageOS 19.1 port
content:
Another week, another unofficial port of LineageOS 19.1 adding support for practically ancient smartphones. This time it’s the turn of the Samsung Galaxy S5, which is getting the very latest build of Android 12L courtesy of an unofficial build of the popular third-party ROM.

more…

The post Android 12L comes to Galaxy S5 via unofficial LineageOS 19.1 port appeared first on 9to5Google.
description: Thanks to an unofficial port of LineageOS 19.1, Android 12L is now available for the Snapdragon version of the 8-year-old Samsung Galaxy S5.
